                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                        <path fill="none" stroke="#3c9e42" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="m2 12l5.25 5l2.625-3M8 12l5.25 5L22 7m-6 0l-3.5 4"/>
                    </svg>
                </i>
                <span>Gestión integral de miembros, aportaciones y transacciones.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-4 items-center transform transition duration-300 hover:scale-105">
                <i> 
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                        <path fill="none" stroke="#3c9e42" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="m2 12l5.25 5l2.625-3M8 12l5.25 5L22 7m-6 0l-3.5 4"/>
                    </svg>
                </i>
                <span>Automatización de procesos financieros y administrativos.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-4 items-center transform transition duration-300 hover:scale-105">
                <i> 
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                        <path fill="none" stroke="#3c9e42" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="m2 12l5.25 5l2.625-3M8 12l5.25 5L22 7m-6 0l-3.5 4"/>
                    </svg>
                </i>
                <span>Seguridad y transparencia en cada operación.</span>
            </li>
