                <i> 
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                        <path fill="none" stroke="#3c9e42" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="m2 12l5.25 5l2.625-3M8 12l5.25 5L22 7m-6 0l-3.5 4"/>
                    </svg>
                </i>
                <span>Soporte y actualización constante para mantenerse al día.</span>
            </li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <!-- Columna derecha: tarjetas -->
    <div class="w-full h-fit lg:w-1/2 flex flex-col items-center gap-8">
        <div class="bg-white border-white border-2 rounded-lg w-full lg:w-1/2 hover:border-blue-800 transform transition lg:-translate-x-28 lg:translate-y-6 xl:-translate-x-32 xl:translate-y-6 2xl:-translate-x-40 2xl:translate-y-6 shadow-xl ">
